latestPosts.caption:
Radha and I on the dance floor.. Radha likes the skin tint and now I like it too!!! 🥰🥰
Hahaha itni khushiiii..🙈
From watching Alia Bhatt on screen to being alongside her and also getting makeup tips from her.. pinch me!! ✨✨
Grateful to create magic with L’Oréal Paris.. it was all worth it ❤

#vishakhapandey #aliabhatt #Ad #InfallibleInMyTint #TintedSerum #SkinTint #LOrealParisIndia #LOrealParis @lorealparis

Guys!!! I shot an Ad with The Salman Khan and can’t express how happy and grateful I am!🥹❤️ I still feel I’m dreaming!🫣
Thank you bhagwaan ji for every thing!🙏
Thu thu thu!🧿🫣

Thank you @tanwarahul.23 for this!✨

#vishakhapandey #salman #salmankhan #dreamcomestrue #ad #newwork

6 Months Already!🥹❤️
and what a journey it’s been!

Grateful beyond words for this special project and the beautiful family that came with it.
The bond we’ve built — constantly in touch, always cheering each other on — is something truly rare and special.

A huge thank you to the amazing @mr_mainra sir  for believing in us and bringing this story to life. Your vision, passion, and calm strength have guided us throughout.
You created not just a show, but a space where we all grew together. Forever grateful.

Here’s to “Gauri” & “Swipe Crime”, to all the memories, and to many more milestones ahead! 💥❤️

#vishakhapandey #versatilemotionpictures #vmp #SwipeCrime #6Months #GratefulHeart #Family
